text: CETI or Ceti may refer to: * the genitive word used to identify the stars belonging to the constellation of Cetus, for example: Tau Ceti * Communication with extraterrestrial intelligence * Communicating Extra-Terrestrial Intelligent * Centro de Enseñanza Técnica Industrial (English) *Centro de Enseñanza Técnica Industrial (Spanish) * Computationally enhanced craft item
title: CETI
